{"tid":485080,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"S8拍照無法對焦 三星\"專業\"回覆","createTime":"2017-11-30T15:43:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-01T20:43:49.000Z","uid":33730,"like":47,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"d6f4a55fef196fdd97037d7aafea1a7ccc534423","tid":485080,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:43:32.000Z","msg":"據外媒Sammboile報導，近日一批三星Galaxy S8用戶在三星官方論壇反饋，在使用S8的過程中遭遇了無法自動對焦的問題，無論使用默認相機應用還是第三方應用(比如Snapchat)都會遇到，十分惱人。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，除了自動對焦無法使用，使用手動對焦也不行，無論你選擇哪種模式拍攝，拍出的照片都是模糊的。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，此前三星曾就此問題發布過聲明，列舉了一些能簡單修復bug的小技巧。如果還是不能湊效，只能送修了。具體如下：<br />\n<br />\n1、確保手機運行最新的系統和應用程式<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2、輕輕敲打手機背部，讓鬆散的元器件回歸原位</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3、清除所有應用緩存和數據<br />\n<br />\n4、恢復工廠設置。<br />\n<br />\n目前，Sammboile已經聯繫三星，以確認該故障到底是硬體還是軟體問題造成。官方尚未回復。"},{"pid":"0d4daed63515cf61a8252a10bf94ed21cff86bc4","tid":485080,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T16:06:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b620bf08636fc45a733be63b31a020d692a943fe","tid":485080,"uid":129658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T16:07:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2eefde84be8b10f68984f0a8e47a2b387d75ffa","tid":485080,"uid":146341,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T16:13:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/01/001244_ffa04f1ed3af0cf12544847b9efbad39.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F01%2F001244_ffa04f1ed3af0cf12544847b9efbad39.jpeg&h=8f41d93f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/c